Bug.WithStack:
Setting the MenuItem text after setting the Menu causes the Menu text to appear
and behave disabled.  This was tested on win2k with all the sp's.  I am running
swt-win32-2133.  Simple example:

Shell shell = new Shell();
Menu menu = new Menu(shell, SWT.BAR);
MenuItem fileItem = new MenuItem(menu, SWT.CASCADE);
Menu fileMenu = new Menu(fileItem);
